## Conclusion

By analyzing annual refugee data alongside global events, our study reveals how geopolitical conflicts, natural disasters, and economic changes drive global displacement patterns. This comprehensive examination underscores the urgency of addressing the root causes of forced migration and the importance of informed humanitarian responses. Data-driven insights are crucial for shaping policies that effectively tackle the increasing challenges of displacement worldwide.

